    <div class="faq-a" id="how-many-emails-should-i-send-in-a-follow-up-seque"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Send 4 to 6 emails over 7 to 14 days for estimate follow-ups. Send 2 to 3 emails for appointment reminders. Send 3 to 4 emails over 11 months for post-service rebooking. The key is persistence without pressure. Each email should add value, not just repeat the same request.</p></div></div>
